  "detailed_description": "Adventure Light is a <strong>beautiful </strong>and very <strong>atmospheric puzzle side-scrolling</strong> game about the boy with the <strong>magic lantern</strong> in the mysterious and dark forest. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1628300/extras/44e60ecdcacc729fbee535ef38b7d2e6.poster.avif?t=1726864029\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1628300/extras/44e60ecdcacc729fbee535ef38b7d2e6.webm?t=1726864029\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1628300/extras/44e60ecdcacc729fbee535ef38b7d2e6.mp4?t=1726864029\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The main concept around which the major part of the game is built, is the idea of <strong>teleportation</strong>. There are several basic types of teleportation devices and objects implemented in the game, utilizing which the player is able to solve many <strong>interesting puzzles</strong>. One of the devices is a magic lantern that the player is carrying around. With its help, the player gets the ability to place a special mark anywhere in the world and <strong>teleport back to it at any time</strong> later.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1628300/extras/0f07daa142ed963ec7da15c981538994.poster.avif?t=1726864029\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1628300/extras/0f07daa142ed963ec7da15c981538994.webm?t=1726864029\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1628300/extras/0f07daa142ed963ec7da15c981538994.mp4?t=1726864029\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Pocket teleporter:</strong> put a mark at a desirable place and teleport back whenever you need.<br></li><li><strong>Static two-way teleports:</strong> use anomalies such as a wormhole to travel between two places in an instant.<br></li><li><strong>Throwable teleport mark:</strong> use a special magic gem to get to all the <strong>secret places</strong> in the mystical forest.<br></li><li><strong>Teleport-based puzzles:</strong> combine the power of different teleports to solve intricate puzzles.<br></li><li><strong>Interactive world:</strong> manipulate numerous puzzle elements to unravel the mystery and move forward.<br></li><li><strong>Collectible items</strong> which will have you peek into the most unexpected <strong>hidden areas</strong> along your journey.<br></li><li><strong>Immersive environment:</strong> dark and beautiful atmosphere will help you better immerse yourself in the mysterious world.<br></li><li><strong>Dark and mystique music </strong> composed by Marcello Colombo, perfectly fits in the game world.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1628300/extras/328afed53e51e39a9440a01044801c45.avif?t=1726864029\" width=616 height=160 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1628300/extras/3b3090623b1598f8418cc35276c31e50.avif?t=1726864029\" width=616 height=130 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1628300/extras/3ca980446dcca8378da320cb0508dcf8.avif?t=1726864029\" width=616 height=150 /></span>",
